证据片段: Mechanical tests were conducted on irradiated Zircaloy-4. The cladding and guide tube material chemistry was consistent with ASTM Alloy Designation UNS R60804. The initial hydrogen concentration was typically less than 15 ppm. The fuel cladding was in a coldworked and stress-relief-annealed condition, while the guide tubes were in a recrystallizedannealed condition.
